IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. LOANCALCULATOR.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 LOAN-AMOUNT          PIC 9(8)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
01 ANNUAL-INTEREST-RATE PIC 9(3)V9(5) VALUE ZEROS.
01 LOAN-TERM            PIC 9(2) VALUE ZEROS.
01 MONTHLY-INTEREST-RATE PIC 9(3)V9(7) VALUE ZEROS.
01 MONTHLY-PAYMENT      PIC 9(8)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
01 NUM-PAYMENTS         PIC 9(3) VALUE ZEROS.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
BEGIN.
    DISPLAY "Enter loan amount (e.g., 50000.00): ".
    ACCEPT LOAN-AMOUNT.
    DISPLAY "Enter annual interest rate (e.g., 5.25): ".
    ACCEPT ANNUAL-INTEREST-RATE.
    DISPLAY "Enter loan term in years (e.g., 15): ".
    ACCEPT LOAN-TERM.

    COMPUTE MONTHLY-INTEREST-RATE = ANNUAL-INTEREST-RATE / 1200.
    COMPUTE NUM-PAYMENTS = LOAN-TERM * 12.
    COMPUTE MONTHLY-PAYMENT = LOAN-AMOUNT * MONTHLY-INTEREST-RATE /
        (1 - (1 + MONTHLY-INTEREST-RATE) ** -NUM-PAYMENTS).

    DISPLAY "Monthly Payment: ", MONTHLY-PAYMENT.

    STOP RUN.
